###############################################################################
#                                                                             #
# Trilinos Release 11.2 Changelog                                             #
#                                                                             #
###############################################################################

Release update 11.2.5 July 11, 2013

1. SEACAS    - Fix parallel-aware exodus build activation

2. Teuchos   - Fix configuration issue on OSX with case sensitive file system

Release update 11.2.4 June 20, 2013

1. ML        - Add support for ParMETIS 4.x and METIS 5.x

2. Teuchos   - Fix cdotc_ declarations

3. Triutils  - Fix issue with ambiguous abs() calls in 64bit.

Release update 11.2.3 April 25, 2013

1. EpetraExt - Fix reindexing with the row and column GID set is not the same.

2. EpetraExt - Fixed singleton filter to not generate a separate linear problem
               if no singletons are detected.

3. Intrepid  - MiniTensor: Fixed coeffcients of Pade Approximant for the
               exponential.
